          "date": "2012-07-23 14:09:51.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-1442 llite: cleanup if a page failed to add into cache",
        "message": "LU-1442 llite: cleanup if a page failed to add into cache\n\nIn lustre, we assume that a dirty page must be queued in osc cache\nfor writing. However, in vvp_io_commit_write(), if a page failed to\nadd into cache, page dirty flag isn't cleared this will cause the\npage will never be added into cache again.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I1c132c6f1d4f5845682e51850eb895b292fc5f0d\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
